title: Avenged Sevenfold  Live Setlist from Hail To The King Tour 2013
description:
Avenged Sevenfold - "Live Setlist - Hail To The King Tour"[Fall 2013]



Setlist based on concerts from Oct./Nov. 2013(source: www.setlist.fm):


Oct 26 - Mandalay Bay Events Center Las Vegas, USA
Nov 6 - Hartwall Areena, Helsinki, Finland
Nov 8 - Hovet, Stockholm, Sweden
Nov 9 - Oslo Spektrum, Oslo, Norway


[**all had the same setlist; so could be expected on future events on 'Euro 2013' tour**]



** All tracks are mp3/320kbps except the ones from Nightmare that are in FLAC(playable with winamp, foobar2000 etc.) **
